item.title: Need help for making a hamachi server!
item.dc:creator: @vegies vegies
item.description:
@vegies wrote:

Step 1: Ok Download Hamachi
Step 2: At The Bottom Of The Window You Will See A Small Triangle
Step 3: Click It
Step 4: Click Create New Server Or Something Like That
Step 5: Then Type Your Wanted Server Name And Password
Step 6: Then Click Ok

Then Your Done :Dâ€¦Hope I Helped
